    // combinational logic + a flop), run each pass in the gate-§5
    // ordering above, assert cell-count / type-mix invariants at each
    // step. dfflibmap + abc_map use mock cell library until liberty.hexa
    // and abc_map.hexa land.
    println("stdlib/yosys/passes.hexa: TBD-STUB (rfc_006 §4 module-3)");
